'''Chuck Hamilton''' is a ''[[Star Wars]]'' fan who designed [[N'Kata Del Gormo/Legends|N'Kata Del Gormo]] and the [[Hysalrian/Legends|Hysalrian]] in the [[Design An Alien]] contest held in the ''[[Star Wars Galaxy Magazine]]s''. The entry was given an honorable mention in the sixteen years and older category. He was twenty-three at the time his entry was published.

